data.title: MIPI Alliance Manufacturer ID Page
data.text: ** Note: Unless noted with [square braces], all companies in the Non-Members and Affiliates table are non-members of MIPI Alliance. Those companies noted with [square braces], however, are affiliates of active member companies. Per the MIPI Bylaws, "Affiliate" means any corporation, partnership, or other entity that, directly or indirectly, owns, is owned by, or is under common ownership with, such Member hereto, for so long as such ownership exists. For the purposes of the foregoing, "own," "owned," or "ownership" shall mean ownership of more than fifty (50%) of the stock or other equity interests entitled to vote for the election of directors or an equivalent governing body of an entity that is directly or indirectly controlled by, under common control with or that controls the subject party.
